      "startTime": 193.1598518931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-ymk005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、その時はよろしくね",
      "startTime": 193.1598518931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.3598498587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……けど、本当に寂しいわね\nもう明後日には東京に帰るだなんて",
      "startTime": 202.1269193491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "明日はオフだし、ゆっくり観光でもどうです？\nといっても、札幌市内はあらかた回っちゃいましたけど",
      "startTime": 209.4602526825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_karaokeroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "karaokeroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.3388296688
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
